itunes:title: Life Advice
title: Life Advice
description: We may not be experts at everything but we're here to give you our opinions (and hopefully some sound life advice) regarding all of your biggest life questions! From letting go of the bitterness of divorce and dating must-haves to our least favorite things about each other and what TV show Stew wants to live in full time. It's good stuff! Tune in and hopefully, you'll snag a little wisdom along the way!
